### **Why This Works**
The pre-built index is generated once during data preparation and stored in binary format. Loading it via mmap is orders of magnitude faster than building it from 15M rows in parallel. This is a **plan-level optimization** (Rule 2 from query-planning.md: use pre-built indexes when available).

